name: Shutter Speed
description:
Street art in London, like it is in many cities, is often related to current affairs. The latest crisis or scandal in the news. Imaginative and clever, it’s never around for long. Like the ever changing news, this art is often replaced by the next big story. These pieces have all appeared on London’s streets over the last few years, but now they’re gone, and this is your chance to own a piece of the ever changing street art…
Dimensions: 3000 x 2000 240dpi jpeg
